Package: gsf
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Stochastic Frontier Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Antigravity
Maintainer: Antigravity <antigravity@example.com>
Description: Implements the Generalized Stochastic Frontier (GSF) model with input-specific inefficiencies as described in Kumbhakar and Tsionas (2021). Supports both a custom Gibbs sampler (default) following the paper's methodology and Stan's HMC/NUTS via 'rstan'.
